- --> NOTE THIS PROGRAM WILL HANG YOUR MACHINE <--

/*
**
** $VER: NewIconGad PLUGIN V1.00 (08-Feb-98) - By Fabio Rotondo
**
** Name         : NewIconGad PLUGIN
**
