Levas wrote:
>
> It is not real serial, it is keyboard... :) two lines: KBD data and KBD
clock
>
> KBD CLK:1111111111111111111010101010101010101010111111111111111
> KBD DAT:1111111111111111111000000111111001111000001111111111111
