> SO I still have some questions: How to stop Amiga multiprocesing for few =
mS
> because I receive random errors (Lost of few bits)

Disable()
=2E..
Enable()

Disable() disables task switching and interrupts; Forbid() only disables
task switching.

Be careful that Wait() enables everything until the signal is received and
that there is absolutely no way out if you get an infinite loop inside.

